{"tid":661623,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"熊本 阿蘇火山 依家仲值唔值得去","createTime":"2018-05-11T17:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T09:10:00.000Z","uid":172085,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac6449a92b99b2e4efd08d5a946a5a1181de13ca","tid":661623,"uid":172085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T17:36:29.000Z","msg":"地震之後 無左纜車 天空之路爛埋 去光山既方法都復雜左<br />\n有無人呢排去過 覺得點 睇唔睇到 個中岳火山口？<br />\n<br />\n除左坐 阿蘇男孩 會方便d （得星期六日）<br />\n但我要係博多去 咁就要坐去大分 先坐到阿蘇男孩<br />\n<br />\n一係就諗住 <br />\n<br />\n博多坐 新幹線 去熊本駅<br />\n再坐電車去 熊本交通中心 再坐大巴到阿蘇（110分鐘）<br />\n係阿蘇 再坐大巴上阿蘇山西駅（30分鐘）<br />\n大巴既錢 要$4000<br />\nJr 就買左 pass<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求意見"},{"pid":"3283f42aa0f303c6d96c0b61f4aa7f64d2d164d8","tid":661623,"uid":148541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T18:28:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adc7138deb34d2f1502b5f0905ec903929c537e7","tid":661623,"uid":120501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:00:42.000Z","msg":"咁樣去又晒時間又唔抵<br />\n個人意見"},{"pid":"49bdfc614a82f5e9c6cdcf0748c178269848d58f","tid":661623,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3283f42aa0f303c6d96c0b61f4aa7f64d2d164d8","tid":661623,"uid":148541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T18:28:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}